"<p>Bitcoin is <a href=\"https://bitcoin.org/en/faq#is-bitcoin-anonymous\">not\n"
"anonymous</a>.</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"<p>Bitcoin ist <a href=\"https://bitcoin.org/en/faq#is-bitcoin-anonymous\">nicht\n"
